    • Constructor Detail

      • EventProcessorChain

        public EventProcessorChain(XMLEventProcessor first,
                   XMLEventProcessor second)
        Creates a chain from two event processors. You should call reset() before using the chain to make sure that events initially generated by the first processor are received by the second one.
        Parameters:
        first - the processor that will receive external input and produce output for the second processor
        second - the processor that will receive input from the first processor produce the output for this aggregate
